---
source: crates/loom/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: "loom_help(&[\"msg\"])"
---
Resolve outstanding `loom:clarify` and `loom:blocked` beads

Usage: loom msg [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -w, --workspace <PATH>  Workspace root. Defaults to the current working directory
  -A, --agent <BACKEND>   Override the agent backend for this invocation [possible values: claude, pi]
  -h, --help              Print help

Workflow:
  -s, --spec <LABEL>  Filter to a specific spec label
  -n <N>              Select bead by 1-based index in the printed list
  -i <ID>             Select bead by id
  -a <CHOICE>         Fast-reply: integer chooses option N for clarify beads; anything else (and any choice for blocked beads) is stored verbatim
  -d                  Dismiss the bead (write canonical note + remove the loom:* label)
